title: Flight Simulator 2020 -  MSFS Update - Spotting Windows 11 colored POI'S: New York and Seattle
description:
Asobo has released Sim Update VI today. As part of the update multiple POI's are colored in Windows 11 blue to celebrate the release of the new OS from Microsoft. In this video we are going to search for those buildings while flying over New York and Seattle
